{
  "stem": "21004.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's the same time, 1942-- April, 1942, I arrived there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the food was very little.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The soup was very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to get packages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Once in a while, they let in, you know, dry, dry bread my mother used to send me, and also another aunt sent me from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then it came, it came to the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was going on for a long time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used to cut-- when somebody was sending bread, they have to cut the bread, see, and see if there's no money.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you can buy nothing for money there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there's tobacco.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And most of the time, they send tobacco.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have a tobacco cigarette, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was smoking was very good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So used to cut it, take out whatever what's in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Ukrainian police-- it was all Ukrainian police-- watching us and doing that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they treat very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, the Ukrainians, they were the worst.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were the worst beating ups.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they started--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when you stay on the road and you don't do the work, you straighten out, they go right away with the whip and beat you.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the way it happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the beginning, we have to go in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took us with a truck in the mountains, get to the mountains, chop with the hammers from the mountains stones, chop them in small pieces with the hammers, put them on carriages, bring them up on top, put them on the trucks, bring them to the roads-- lined up the whole, how many miles, you know, road.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But later they took-- we, we have to take out the old stones.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have to take out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was very hard to pick out the old stones.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
